{"tid":1454061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇文宣可以諗到做d嘢？我覺得唔可以唔理，大家點睇？","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:27:49.000Z","uid":279497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf625c75a4437931794f6fa92dbf56a13e6d40f5","tid":1454061,"uid":279497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"E+共匪正鋪天蓋地在罵香港，成日宣傳得小數人破壞香港，吹噓攪港獨，微博微訊唔駛講日日都係咁吹。<br />\n仲有將光頭黑警慈悲化，將佢變成被害者。<br />\n入面我哋唔理，但外國一d長久嘅華人（唔係芝麻移民），希望佢哋清楚知道香港真正問題。唔好比共匪繼續洗腦，應該要正視。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得大肥講得啱<br />\n[url]://youtu.be/gjJN229V4gE[/url]<br />\n鳳凰衛視將黑警問題誣陷示威者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGMPLZ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGMPLZ0.png&h=ff93f429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將光頭黑警神化<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvvUcG5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvvUcG5.png&h=85faaf97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量水軍誣陷示威者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ly5H52u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLy5H52u.png&h=f4a22b14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kQkSHA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kQkSHA.png&h=10dbe16c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpr0SHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkpr0SHD.png&h=2b9770b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFA81A1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFA81A1.png&h=d72d1850&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADVQvuq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADVQvuq.png&h=c24e4e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cC0UcHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcC0UcHT.png&h=4bee4f63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67q1B9M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu